name: Spiritual peddler
description: This work tells about the number of people who are willing to sell religion for a desire. In this work there is a main object that is carrying a sack that says religion, then on the sack there is a label that says sale depicts a practice in peddling religion. The main object here is made large and prominent as an emphasis on the main object, the expression in this work is conveyed through color and the cultivation of the main object that tends to be spontaneous.
